&lt;p&gt;Its like a memory trail.&amp;nbsp; You must always start with the first square, then the second, then the third and so on. Example: the first square is gorm, press it. Then it will tell you gorm again and then another square like bui.&amp;nbsp; So you must start with gorm and then press bui. Then it will tell you again gorm, bui and then say dhearg. So you again press gorm first then bui and then dhearg.&amp;nbsp; And so the game goes on.&amp;nbsp; I find it quite useful.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I hope this helps&lt;/p&gt;
